## Description {#details}

Meta qualifiers for a value.

Pair of whatever expression is used to qualify the value, and <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a965a7b0afb2678973d155a103b9f55b5">Boolean</a> of whether or not it&#39;s indirect.
